{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Overview</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are only some limited resources left in your aircraft, use these resources to escape the enemy's pursuit.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A training system in the aircraft with different levels, challenge the levels to train your control ability and collect coins to upgrade the aircraft.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>After defeat enemy during training/combat, some useful gems/coins will drop. These gems have different uses to help you survive in space, and the coins can be used to upgrade the aircraft.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Different abilities to help defeat powerful enemy</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>How to Use different weapon to defeat enemies</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Different gems drops from enemies help you survive in space</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/Gems.png?t=1675128424\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect coins to upgrade your abilities to help defeat powerful enemy</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/Upgrade.png?t=1675128424\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You cannot stop the ship, but you can disable the engine of the aircraft that move slowly and missiles don't trace the ship</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/DisableEngineGif.gif?t=1675128424\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Magnetic field changes direction/rebound attack from enemy</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/Magnetic.gif?t=1675128424\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gravity field slows down the attack/object that the ship can avoid them</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/GrivatyGif.gif?t=1675128424\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Trap pulls surrounding object to its centre</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/TrapGif.gif?t=1675128424\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shield can block attack and rebound laser type attack</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/ShieldGif.gif?t=1675128424\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fuel boost the ship</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/FuelGif.gif?t=1675128424\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Bomb clear enemies around the aircraft</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/BombGif.gif?t=1675128424\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1675128424","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/page.bg.jpg?t=1675128424","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1675128424","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1675128424","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Overview</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are only some limited resources left in your aircraft, use these resources to escape the enemy's pursuit.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A training system in the aircraft with different levels, challenge the levels to train your control ability and collect